WEBVTT

00:02:06.040 --> 00:02:06.680
Siniang.

00:02:08.080 --> 00:02:08.680
Siniang.

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:10.639
Who is it?

00:02:11.000 --> 00:02:11.599
It's me.

00:02:12.319 --> 00:02:13.879
I have something to ask Concubine Si.

00:02:26.240 --> 00:02:28.560
Why have you come here to find me?

00:02:29.199 --> 00:02:30.319
I went to your room to find you.

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:31.280
But you weren't there.

00:02:31.879 --> 00:02:33.039
I heard from the Young Master...

00:02:33.039 --> 00:02:34.680
...that you sometimes stay in the Master's room.

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:37.000
So I came here to find you.

00:02:43.360 --> 00:02:44.639
Last night...

00:02:45.400 --> 00:02:46.800
...that Ding Da...

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.719
...was wailing and howling.

00:02:51.800 --> 00:02:53.039
He was so loud...

00:02:53.039 --> 00:02:54.639
...I couldn't sleep at all.

00:02:55.319 --> 00:02:56.360
So...

00:02:58.039 --> 00:03:00.000
...I came here to sleep.

00:03:01.000 --> 00:03:01.919
Since you are awake...

00:03:02.639 --> 00:03:04.120
...put on your clothes and come answer questions.

00:03:05.039 --> 00:03:05.879
My Lord...

00:03:06.439 --> 00:03:07.520
Whatever you have to ask...

00:03:07.719 --> 00:03:09.400
...you can just ask here.

00:03:12.719 --> 00:03:14.360
How do you know I'm an official?

00:03:19.159 --> 00:03:20.840
You're hurting me.

00:03:26.479 --> 00:03:28.840
As soon as Your Honor entered the main hall...

00:03:29.560 --> 00:03:31.120
...I could tell.

00:03:32.560 --> 00:03:35.439
Fierce gaze, dignified bearing...

00:03:36.080 --> 00:03:37.280
...you must be an official.

00:03:38.919 --> 00:03:40.680
You are Yu'er's sister, Huang Cui, right?

00:03:43.080 --> 00:03:44.039
What did you say?

00:03:46.039 --> 00:03:47.520
Concubine Si is a smart woman.

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:49.520
I am giving you a chance now.

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:50.479
You'd best cherish it.

00:03:51.759 --> 00:03:53.000
Cherish...

00:03:54.800 --> 00:03:56.039
Cherish what?

00:03:57.759 --> 00:03:59.000
Cherish...

00:03:59.240 --> 00:04:00.719
...the man before me?

00:04:02.759 --> 00:04:03.719
Put your clothes on first.

00:04:03.719 --> 00:04:04.639
Then I'll come find you.

00:04:23.759 --> 00:04:26.240
Where did you run off to in such a hurry this morning?

00:04:28.720 --> 00:04:29.600
I went to see Siniang.

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:32.040
Siniang is not Huang Cui.

00:04:32.040 --> 00:04:33.120
Obviously, that's impossible.

00:04:33.759 --> 00:04:34.680
Why is it impossible?

00:04:35.199 --> 00:04:36.519
Huang Cui came from a poor background.

00:04:36.839 --> 00:04:37.839
Siniang's figure...

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:39.920
...is not something that can be achieved overnight.

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:42.600
Besides, she used to be the top courtesan at Fengqi Courtyard.

00:04:43.319 --> 00:04:44.560
You're the only one who doesn't know that.

00:04:45.480 --> 00:04:46.160
Then this Siniang...

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:47.720
...why would she be here at Baixiao Villa?

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:50.000
She doesn't look like a guest.

00:04:50.399 --> 00:04:52.399
Nor does she seem like the Master's second wife or concubine.

00:04:56.839 --> 00:04:58.240
She doesn't lack money.

00:04:58.759 --> 00:05:01.519
Dignitaries and nobles have spent fortunes on her.

00:05:02.800 --> 00:05:05.839
What could the Villa Master possibly offer her...

00:05:06.519 --> 00:05:08.680
...to make her stay at the villa so willingly?

00:05:15.480 --> 00:05:16.519
These petitions...

00:05:17.199 --> 00:05:18.240
...were all written by Ye Li.

00:05:19.600 --> 00:05:20.160
Yes.

00:05:20.920 --> 00:05:23.319
He was the top scholar in the twenty-fourth year of Qingde.

00:05:24.199 --> 00:05:26.160
His Majesty intended for him to enter the Hanlin Academy.

00:05:26.160 --> 00:05:27.800
But the lad didn't know what was good for him.

00:05:28.199 --> 00:05:30.480
He actually petitioned the Emperor in open court...

00:05:30.480 --> 00:05:31.920
...to retry the old case of the Chao family.

00:05:31.920 --> 00:05:33.240
In a fit of rage, His Majesty...

00:05:33.240 --> 00:05:35.439
...exiled him to Lingnan to serve as a county official.

00:05:38.160 --> 00:05:39.000
The Chao family?

00:05:39.480 --> 00:05:41.199
The Zhongzhou Censor, Chao Heng.

00:05:42.079 --> 00:05:42.680
Exactly.

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:46.439
Back then, Chao Heng sold the iron mine map to the enemy...

00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:47.920
...with the intent to rebel.

00:05:47.920 --> 00:05:49.079
His entire family was executed.

00:05:49.399 --> 00:05:52.199
Ye Li and Lord Chao's daughter were childhood sweethearts.

00:05:52.439 --> 00:05:54.079
It is said they were even engaged.

00:05:54.240 --> 00:05:56.439
So he is convinced it was a wrongful conviction...

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:58.680
...and has always wanted to clear the Chao family's name.

00:05:59.480 --> 00:06:02.720
Then how did he get from Lingnan to the Capital...

00:06:03.160 --> 00:06:04.720
...and become a litigator for the Capital Governor?

00:06:06.920 --> 00:06:09.639
As it happens, this Ye Li is quite a capable official.

00:06:09.759 --> 00:06:10.600
In less than three years...

00:06:10.920 --> 00:06:13.040
...he took a destitute county...

00:06:13.160 --> 00:06:14.759
...and turned it into a place...

00:06:14.759 --> 00:06:16.759
...where families from miles around came to settle.

00:06:17.920 --> 00:06:19.519
Before the Minister of Revenue left office...

00:06:19.639 --> 00:06:21.439
...he made an exception to transfer him back to the Capital.

00:06:21.920 --> 00:06:24.639
He thought that after years of experience...

00:06:24.639 --> 00:06:25.800
...he would have learned how the world works.

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:28.079
Unexpectedly, as soon as he returned to the Capital...

00:06:28.079 --> 00:06:29.759
...he began campaigning for the Chao family again.

00:06:30.279 --> 00:06:32.040
As a result, he was repeatedly demoted...

00:06:32.199 --> 00:06:34.839
...until he ended up as a litigator for the Capital Governor.

00:06:38.600 --> 00:06:39.600
It seems...

00:06:39.920 --> 00:06:41.759
...we really underestimated this Ye Li.

00:06:48.240 --> 00:06:49.959
Fire! Fire!

00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:51.839
Pass the water!

00:06:52.439 --> 00:06:53.240
Hurry up!

00:06:53.439 --> 00:06:53.879
Over here!

00:06:53.879 --> 00:06:54.480
Okay!

00:06:59.519 --> 00:07:00.439
Water is coming!

00:07:04.680 --> 00:07:05.240
Quick!

00:07:05.319 --> 00:07:06.560
Call more people to fight the fire!

00:07:21.160 --> 00:07:22.160
She's here!

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:24.279
She's here!

00:07:26.360 --> 00:07:26.959
What is going on?

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:32.199
I asked you, what is going on?

00:07:35.480 --> 00:07:37.079
She's here to claim my life!

00:07:37.800 --> 00:07:39.639
She's here to claim my life!

00:07:41.600 --> 00:07:42.920
It's the female ghost in red!

00:07:42.920 --> 00:07:44.040
The female ghost in red!

00:07:47.360 --> 00:07:48.360
The female ghost in red!

00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:51.240
Did you really see it?

00:07:52.920 --> 00:07:53.839
I saw it!

00:07:54.800 --> 00:07:56.079
I saw it!

00:08:02.759 --> 00:08:04.240
Master Kun, guard the door.

00:08:04.240 --> 00:08:05.319
Xiaobai and I will go in and take a look.

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:13.160
If we hadn't happened to be here,

00:08:13.480 --> 00:08:15.839
Ding Da would likely have perished in the fire.

00:08:17.839 --> 00:08:18.560
Smell this.

00:08:19.439 --> 00:08:20.560
Does it smell like lamp oil?

00:08:25.560 --> 00:08:26.439
It really does.

00:08:27.319 --> 00:08:28.959
Ding Da said he saw a female ghost in red.

00:08:29.920 --> 00:08:31.399
But when we rushed over from all sides,

00:08:31.600 --> 00:08:32.519
we didn't see anyone.

00:08:33.799 --> 00:08:36.320
There was no one and no fire in this room,

00:08:37.240 --> 00:08:38.840
so it had to be lit with lamp oil.

00:08:41.799 --> 00:08:43.200
If it wasn't a ghost,

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:46.279
why burn this specific room?

00:08:52.559 --> 00:08:55.039
Destroying the body wasn't enough; they wanted to erase the traces.

00:08:55.399 --> 00:08:56.679
How interesting.

00:09:03.960 --> 00:09:04.679
Young Master.

00:09:05.039 --> 00:09:06.639
Is Ding Da settled in?

00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:08.559
As Doctor Du instructed,

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:09.679
we have sent him back.

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:12.039
We also left guards around the courtyard.

00:09:12.759 --> 00:09:13.799
If anyone approaches,

00:09:14.039 --> 00:09:15.960
please notify us immediately, Young Master.

00:09:16.159 --> 00:09:16.759
All right.

00:09:21.879 --> 00:09:23.879
You suspected Concubine Si last time.

00:09:24.360 --> 00:09:25.600
Shouldn't you apologize to her?

00:09:31.879 --> 00:09:32.679
Concubine Si.

00:09:33.679 --> 00:09:35.480
I offended you earlier.

00:09:35.639 --> 00:09:36.519
I am truly sorry.

00:09:37.639 --> 00:09:38.639
Please accept my apologies.

00:09:48.639 --> 00:09:50.039
Is she angry?

00:09:50.360 --> 00:09:51.399
Or did she forgive you?

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:54.480
Do you believe I'll cut you down right now?

00:10:14.759 --> 00:10:17.399
Cherish the one before you.

00:10:52.960 --> 00:10:55.000
What strange dreams I had.

00:11:00.039 --> 00:11:00.720
Everyone.

00:11:00.960 --> 00:11:03.159
I imagine no one rested well last night.

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:05.240
So I made some side dishes today.

00:11:05.480 --> 00:11:06.399
To help everyone recover.

00:11:06.879 --> 00:11:07.639
Please, everyone.

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:09.480
Wait a moment, everyone.

00:11:15.000 --> 00:11:16.759
Thinking that you didn't sleep well,

00:11:16.759 --> 00:11:18.519
you must have no appetite.

00:11:18.960 --> 00:11:20.399
So I personally cooked,

00:11:20.399 --> 00:11:21.679
and made a plate of crispy fried pork.

00:11:21.679 --> 00:11:23.120
Come, come, have a taste.

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:24.240
Try it.

00:11:24.480 --> 00:11:25.559
I'll help myself then.

00:11:25.960 --> 00:11:28.159
I didn't expect Siniang to be so multi-talented.

00:11:28.759 --> 00:11:30.159
I have plenty more skills than that.

00:11:30.600 --> 00:11:31.639
Do you want to try them?

00:11:40.840 --> 00:11:41.480
Where is Ding Da?

00:11:41.480 --> 00:11:42.559
Him? He's afraid of dying.

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:43.360
He's hiding.

00:11:50.480 --> 00:11:51.240
Young Master.

00:11:51.600 --> 00:11:52.240
Have a taste.

00:11:52.799 --> 00:11:54.000
Thank you, Concubine Si.

00:11:55.759 --> 00:11:56.480
Concubine Si.

00:11:57.000 --> 00:11:57.879
Your skirt hem is dirty.

00:12:01.759 --> 00:12:03.960
I probably got it dirty in the kitchen by mistake.

00:12:06.639 --> 00:12:07.600
Then you all go ahead and eat.

00:12:07.679 --> 00:12:08.720
I'll go change.

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:10.440
The villa hasn't been safe lately.

00:12:10.600 --> 00:12:11.360
I'll go with you.

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:12.320
Thank you.

00:12:15.039 --> 00:12:15.720
Xiaobai.

00:12:16.159 --> 00:12:16.919
You stay here.

00:12:17.159 --> 00:12:18.039
Take good care of everyone.

00:12:18.559 --> 00:12:19.159
Yes.

00:12:25.679 --> 00:12:27.639
Given Siniang's relationship with the Master,

00:12:27.840 --> 00:12:29.559
it's surprising Xu Qingqing is so close to her.

00:12:30.200 --> 00:12:30.960
Everyone.

00:12:32.360 --> 00:12:34.039
How is the deciphering of the code going?

00:12:35.320 --> 00:12:36.559
You're still working on the code?

00:12:37.279 --> 00:12:39.440
I just want to leave this godforsaken place right now.

00:12:39.840 --> 00:12:41.120
Whoever wants this treasure can have it.

00:12:41.600 --> 00:12:42.519
I cherish my life.

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:43.879
Exactly.

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:45.559
A few days ago, regarding the code,

00:12:45.840 --> 00:12:47.240
Ding Da was the most vocal about it.

00:12:47.639 --> 00:12:48.519
Look at him now.

00:12:48.799 --> 00:12:49.919
He's been scared out of his wits.

00:12:51.039 --> 00:12:52.440
I really am clumsy.

00:12:53.159 --> 00:12:54.080
Just cooking a meal,

00:12:54.360 --> 00:12:55.919
and I got my skirt dirty.

00:12:56.200 --> 00:12:56.919
Siniang.

00:12:56.919 --> 00:12:58.000
It really was hard work for you.

00:12:58.519 --> 00:12:59.519
No need to be polite.

00:13:03.759 --> 00:13:04.320
Brother Liu.

00:13:05.039 --> 00:13:06.120
Are you not afraid?

00:13:08.360 --> 00:13:09.240
What do I have to be afraid of?

00:13:09.960 --> 00:13:11.240
I didn't kidnap anyone's brother.

00:13:11.960 --> 00:13:12.879
So you're not afraid, huh?

00:13:13.240 --> 00:13:15.200
If you're not afraid, hurry up and help find the murderer.

00:13:15.480 --> 00:13:17.080
Only when the murderer is caught,

00:13:17.480 --> 00:13:19.879
can we look for the treasure in peace, right?

00:13:30.279 --> 00:13:31.480
There are guards in the courtyard.

00:13:31.840 --> 00:13:33.039
Why is there a need to lock the door?

00:13:35.519 --> 00:13:36.519
Young Master.

00:13:37.000 --> 00:13:38.399
With a status like mine,

00:13:39.200 --> 00:13:40.480
an extra layer of caution

00:13:41.440 --> 00:13:43.120
means one less piece of gossip.

00:13:49.519 --> 00:13:50.240
Please.